=head1 DESCRIPTION

Returns the relevance scores at these audience sizes when used in the
GetAudienceGenerationJob for a specified audience generation job and
configured audience model.

Specifies the list of allowed C<audienceSize> values when used in the
StartAudienceExportJob for an audience generation job. You can use the
C<ABSOLUTE> AudienceSize to configure out audience sizes using the
count of identifiers in the output. You can use the C<Percentage>
AudienceSize to configure sizes in the range 1-100 percent.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> AudienceSizeBins => ArrayRef[Int]

An array of the different audience output sizes.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> AudienceSizeType => Str

Whether the audience output sizes are defined as an absolute number or
a percentage.



